# Deliberate exception: a frozen snapshot committed for the hosted Streamlit
# Cloud demo (Forecast tab only), since that deployment gets a fresh clone
# with no local dbt-built warehouse. Regenerate via the README's dbt steps
# if it drifts from the real pipeline output; this is a snapshot, not a
# substitute for actually running dbt.
!data/warehouse.duckdb

# dbt
dbt/demandcast/target/
dbt/demandcast/dbt_packages/
dbt/demandcast/logs/
profiles.yml

